research/history/logs/agent_action_0036.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":35,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}。其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个静态 expert 子库 e(x)，并只在该子库内做 local top-k 得到 α_{e,i}(x)。因此它可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”推理链路，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。相对 r35 仅改 K: 128 -> 160，回答一个结构问题：在 lowrank+expert 这个新 family 中，适度增加 sparse residual 容量后，FVU 是否会比 plain expert_topk 的同成本邻域下降更快，从而证明 trunk+expert 组合值得继续推进。","summary":"继续验证新 family `lowrank_expert_topk`，不回到 old-family 微调。以 r35 为参考只提高 `K` 到 160，在仍低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x 总成本的前提下，检查 lowrank trunk + local expert residual 是否开始形成比 `expert_topk` 更有竞争力的中低成本 Pareto 斜率。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束；相对 r35 仅修改 `K`。这是对刚引入的新结构做最小必要的第二个锚点，而不是回到 plain selector 的局部扫点。按当前成本估算，`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 的 total_cost 约 0.69x，仍在预算内，且能直接回答该 family 是否具有继续扩展价值。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_topk K=160` 相对 r35 出现清晰 FVU 改善且斜率优于 `expert_topk`，下一轮仍保持 family 不变，只改 `K` 到 192，确认该 family 在 0.8x 附近是否继续沿 Pareto 前进。","如果 `K=160` 仍无明显收益，则应停止继续打磨该两段式原型，优先转向 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`，而不是退回 plain `topk/jumprelu/factorized_topk`。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","当前已完成新 family 首轮验证；Round 36 只补第二个 K 锚点，目标是判断 lowrank+expert 的 FVU-cost 斜率，而不是刷新全局最低 FVU。","成本估算：`lowrank_expert_topk, EF=1, K=160` 约为 total 0.69x（selection 0.22x + deployment 0.47x），显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也低于当前最佳可行点 0.75x。","若该点仍弱，应把后续结构预算转向三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 或 `two-stage residual expert`。"],"touched_files":[]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0249.json:7:  "family_name": "product_key_expert_jumprelu",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0249.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E_pk(x)} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e^\u03c4(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\u3002\u5176\u4e2d {b_{e,i}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff0cE_pk(x) \u7531\u4e24\u8def product-key router \u7ed9\u51fa\uff1alogit_e(x)=l_{a(e)}(x)+r_{b(e)}(x)\uff0c\u518d\u9009\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff1bexpert \u5185\u4ecd\u7528 JumpReLU \u5f62\u6210\u5c40\u90e8 support\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u5bfc\u51fa\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201cleft/right product-key \u6253\u5206 -> \u9009\u62e9\u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 sparse support -> \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u548c -> \u9009\u62e9\u6027\u8865\u507f\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` \u5224\u5b9a\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9 family \u4ecd\u4e0d\u5f97\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d objective leaderboard\u3002\u57fa\u4e8e\u5f53\u524d\u8fd0\u884c\u65f6\u72b6\u6001\uff0cround 248 \u5df2\u628a\u517c\u5bb9 incumbent \u66f4\u65b0\u4e3a `product_key_expert_jumprelu K=32 NUM_EXPERTS=1024 LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\uff0cruntime frontier objective\u22480.30515\uff0c\u4e14 r248 \u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u95ee\u9898\u5df2\u4e0d\u662f cost \u4e0d\u591f\u4f4e\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u66f4\u5927 bank \u5e26\u6765\u7684 throughput regression \u4e0b\u8fd8\u6ca1\u628a exceed \u518d\u538b\u7a7f 0.30 \u95e8\u69db\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r248 \u672c\u8f6e\u53ea\u628a `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` \u4ece `160` \u964d\u5230 `128`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=product_key_expert_jumprelu`\u3001`K=32`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u6d4b\u8bd5\u201c\u66f4\u5927\u7684 total bank \u5df2\u7ecf\u6210\u7acb\u540e\uff0c\u662f\u5426\u53ef\u4ee5\u628a micro-expert \u518d\u538b\u7a84\u4e00\u6863\uff0c\u7528\u66f4\u4f4e selection cost \u4fdd\u4f4f\u5927\u90e8\u5206 exceed \u4f18\u52bf\u201d\u3002\u6309\u672c\u5730\u7cbe\u786e\u6210\u672c\u590d\u6838\uff0c\u8be5\u70b9 `selection_accesses=327680`\u3001`deployment_accesses=163840`\u3001`combined_accesses=491520`\u3001exact `total_cost_ratio=0.1171875`\uff1b\u5728\u5f53\u524d runtime \u8bb0\u5206\u53e3\u5f84\u4e0b\u7ea6\u8bb0\u4e3a `0.12x`\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u53ea\u8981 `exceed_alpha_0.50` \u7ef4\u6301\u5728\u7ea6 `0.185` \u5de6\u53f3\u6216\u66f4\u4f4e\uff0c\u5c31\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u7ee7\u7eed\u5237\u65b0\u5f53\u524d incumbent\u3002",
